European Central Bank's  Weber Says Region Isn't Facing a Currency Crisis

-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 
2011-04-11T16:49:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/european-central-bank-s-weber-says-region-isn-t-facing-a-currency-crisis.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member  Axel Weber  said the euro region isn’t facing a
currency crisis.  “The euro is a credible currency,” Weber said during a
panel discussion in Bochum,  Germany  today. “We’re not facing a
crisis of the currency but a crisis of debt in individual member
countries.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jana Randow at 
 jrandow@bloomberg.net  